# 🧩 Step 1 — MVP (Version 1 you will ACTUALLY ship)

## 🎯 Goal:

Launch in **7–10 days**, not perfection

## 🔥 MVP Features (strict)

* Script-based widget (`<script src=...>`)
* Accept / Reject / Customize
* Save consent (cookie + localStorage)
* Category-based (analytics, marketing)
* Simple UI (clean, fast)
* Callback hook (`onConsentChange`)

👉 That’s it. No overengineering.

